e</a>与<a href="https://honeyworks.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">HoneyWorks</a>合作专辑《 <a href="https://www.joysound.com/web/s/campaign/1336/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Horohanigaoka High School</a> 》发行，“hololive x HoneyWorks x JOYSOUND 合作活动”将于3月31日（星期日）23点59分举行。</p><p>您可以在全国安装了目标型号的卡拉 OK 店以及卡拉 OK 应用程序“解析评分 JOYSOUND”参加此活动。通过抽选，获得由签名者亲笔签名的《Horohanigaoka High School》普通版 CD 一张。会员们，共有15人将收到礼物。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000002305.000004747.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">兴股份有限公司新闻稿</a></p><h2>VTuber经纪公司“FIRST STAGE PRODUCTION”第3期出道</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/59941a1510a182f52b8dc98b1708a302-kix.r07pjko0bh7i-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/59941a1510a182f52b8dc98b1708a302-kix.r07pjko0bh7i-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/59941a1510a182f52b8dc98b1708a302-kix.r07pjko0bh7i-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/59941a1510a182f52b8dc98b1708a302-kix.r07pjko0bh7i-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/59941a1510a182f52b8dc98b1708a302-kix.r07pjko0bh7i-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/59941a1510a182f52b8dc98b1708a302-kix.r07pjko0bh7i-jpg.webp 1280w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> REALITY Studios Co., Ltd.运营的VTuber经纪公司“ <a href="https://twitter.com/1stpro_official" target="_blank" rel="noopener">FIRST STAGE PRODUCTION</a> ”的第三代人才将首次亮相。</p><p>首次登场的<a href="https://twitter.com/Endoluphy_fsp" target="_blank" rel="noopener">有Endolphy☆Mi</a> 、<a href="https://twitter.com/Waraku_fsp" target="_blank" rel="noopener">座敷之翔</a>、宗田<a href="https://twitter.com/SodaCosmo_fsp" target="_blank" rel="noopener">小相扑</a>、<a href="https://twitter.com/Guiltychan_fsp" target="_blank" rel="noopener">大罪恶魔Gilty-chan</a> 、<a href="https://twitter.com/Tsumugihime_fsp" target="_blan