-kix.xyu6e2p89cb2-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.xyu6e2p89cb2-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.xyu6e2p89cb2-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.xyu6e2p89cb2-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.xyu6e2p89cb2-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.wg1b5dp9y6iy-1-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.wg1b5dp9y6iy-1-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.wg1b5dp9y6iy-1-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.wg1b5dp9y6iy-1-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.wg1b5dp9y6iy-1-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.wg1b5dp9y6iy-1-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.wg1b5dp9y6iy-1-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>浦良七海演唱了多首原创歌曲，正如她所说：“今天我想给大家分享我原创歌曲中的各种‘可爱’歌曲！”</p><p>她的快节奏首张单曲《 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V5ts_cYW_h4" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Diayanokagayaki》</strong></a>和她的第一首原创歌曲《 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NYco0gywi00" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Atashi World</strong></a> 》均由她亲自绘制插图。从<span style="color: rgba(19.00000155, 19.00000155, 19.00000155);">可以欣赏和弦VSinger多样音色的</span>《暧昧的<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w7a0wwSy7Is" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>奇迹人生</strong></a>》，到酷炫优美的第二张单曲《 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TyJ_q_FOkIc" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Trigger</strong></a> 》。</p><p>他们以一月份刚刚发行的《 <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N-4cXU_lU8U" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Kiwamete Kawaii</strong></a> 》结束了30分钟的舞台。我觉得这是一个奢侈的时刻，她的表演和MC充分利用了她的时间，即使是第一次听说她的人也能感受到她的魅力。</p><h2>稻叶羽流</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.cs31964o5kmh-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.cs31964o5kmh-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.cs31964o5kmh-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.cs31964o5kmh-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.cs31964o5kmh-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.cs31964o5kmh-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.cs31964o5kmh-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>这是<a href="https://twitter.com/Haneru_Inaba" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>稻叶羽的</strong></a>第三次亮相，她也被称为三丽鸥的超级粉丝。 </p><div class="mg-mogura-card m-0 mb-2 mb-md-3"><div class="d-flex"><div class="mg-mogura-card-thumb position-relative"><img class="mg-img-cover position-absolute h-100 w-100" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2021/12/202112131213648000-300x169.jpg"></div><div class="card-body mg-card-text p-2 p-lg-3"><h3 class="h6 mt-0 mw-0 mb-1 p-0 card-title mg-card-title mg-text-break-all text-dark font-weight-normal"> VTuber Inaba Haneru 参观虚拟“三丽鸥彩虹乐园” 您有何感想？</h3><div class="text-gray mg-mogura-card-excerpt mb-1 my-md-2"> 12月12日（星期日），Animare旗下VTuber Haneru Inaba在VRChat上对参观“三丽鸥彩虹乐园”进行了YouTube直播。许多 VRChat 用户见到 Haneru Inaba 并表达了他们的惊讶 [&amp;hel...</div> <span class="badge badge-outline-live mg-mogura-card-badge px-2">VTuber</span> <span class="text-muted small ml-1">2021.12.13</span></div></div></div><p>在过去的现场表演中，她表现出了对Pompompurin的热爱，并在Virtual Puro舞台上演唱了许多Sanrio歌曲，但这次她以Cinnamoroll的“ <strong>Chu-Chu-Chu</strong> ”开始。在MC期间，他在谈论他对布丁君的喜爱时，继续演唱Beatcats的《 <strong>ZigZag Love</strong> 》，他称Beatcats是“我现在最喜欢的三丽鸥乐队”。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.6vxv85ecxslx-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.6vxv85ecxslx-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.6vxv85ecxslx-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.6vxv85ecxslx-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.6vxv85ecxslx-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.6vxv85ecxslx-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.6vxv85ecxslx-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.b1y6tc5bfl7d-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.b1y6tc5bfl7d-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.b1y6tc5bfl7d-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.b1y6tc5bfl7d-300x169.webp 300w, h