地、名産品を3D再現しており「倉吉がどういった魅力のある街なのか」を、バーチャルで体感しながら学べます。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/97f6dc900daf500208d6f84afd70da90-kix.o15fxx6ksz1c-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/97f6dc900daf500208d6f84afd70da90-kix.o15fxx6ksz1c-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/97f6dc900daf500208d6f84afd70da90-kix.o15fxx6ksz1c-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/97f6dc900daf500208d6f84afd70da90-kix.o15fxx6ksz1c-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/97f6dc900daf500208d6f84afd70da90-kix.o15fxx6ksz1c-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/97f6dc900daf500208d6f84afd70da90-kix.z3xcics5e1iy-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/97f6dc900daf500208d6f84afd70da90-kix.z3xcics5e1iy-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/97f6dc900daf500208d6f84afd70da90-kix.z3xcics5e1iy-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/97f6dc900daf500208d6f84afd70da90-kix.z3xcics5e1iy-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/97f6dc900daf500208d6f84afd70da90-kix.z3xcics5e1iy-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/97f6dc900daf500208d6f84afd70da90-kix.whr3x4o7rsvp-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/97f6dc900daf500208d6f84afd70da90-kix.whr3x4o7rsvp-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/97f6dc900daf500208d6f84afd70da90-kix.whr3x4o7rsvp-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/97f6dc900daf50